graph LR
    subgraph "CI Infrastructure"
        Jobs[CI Jobs<br/>Periodic/Rehearse/Pull-CI]
        GCS[Prow GCS<br/>JUnit XML Artifacts<br/>gcsweb-qe-private-deck-ci]
    end

    subgraph "Dashboard Pod"
        Collector[Data Collectors<br/>prow_gcs.py<br/>Parses JUnit XML]
        DB[(SQLite Database<br/>PVC: /data/dashboard.db<br/><br/>Tables:<br/>- job_runs<br/>- test_results<br/>- ai_analyses<br/>- daily_metrics)]
        Flask[Flask Web Server<br/>API Endpoints]

        Collector --> DB
        DB --> Flask
    end

    subgraph "Scheduled Collection"
        CronJob[CronJob<br/>Every 6 hours]
        JobPod[Job Pod<br/>Runs Collector]

        CronJob -.Spawns.- JobPod
        JobPod --> Collector
    end

    subgraph "User Interactions"
        Browser[Web Browser]
        Modal[Test Detail Modal]
    end

    subgraph "External Integrations"
        AI[Vertex AI<br/>Claude Sonnet 4<br/>Failure Analysis]
        JIRA[Jira API<br/>Ticket Creation<br/>Duplicate Detection]
    end

    Jobs --> GCS
    GCS -->|HTTP Fetch<br/>JUnit XML| Collector

    Browser -->|HTTPS| Flask
    Flask -->|JSON/HTML| Browser
    Browser --> Modal

    Modal -->|Analyze Failure| AI
    AI -->|Root Cause<br/>Component<br/>Confidence| DB

    Modal -->|Create Ticket| JIRA
    JIRA -->|Ticket Key<br/>WINC-1866| DB

    Modal -->|Save Classification| DB
    DB -->|Load Existing<br/>Jira/AI/Classification| Modal

    style DB fill:#99ccff
    style AI fill:#ffccff
    style JIRA fill:#ffccff
    style Jobs fill:#ccffcc
    style CronJob fill:#ffffcc
    style JobPod fill:#ffffcc
